{
  "stem": "19111.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 222.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He came to Vilna sometimes during the-- the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after the Germans entered Vilna, he met-- he came from Vienna, Austria.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was an Austrian person from Austria.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when the Germans entered, he found one of the German soldiers that was there was a friend of his that he grew up with from Vienna, Austria.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they got to talking to each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that Oscar Gluck was actually a Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But his friend convinced him that he can get him the job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was put in charge of the Kailis factory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was given false documentation that he was a Volksdeutsch-- in other words, that he's a German, that he came out of Austria.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was living under the disguise of a German, a real German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was-- he actually came from Austria.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at one point, there was a fire in the factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was some investigation by the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And during the investigation, as they were investigating, they discovered that this Oscar Gluck is a Jew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they arrested him and his wife, and they shot them to death immediately on the spot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he was actually the head of the Kailis factory for some time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And was there a committee of Jews in Kailis also working in the factory or helping to run the factory, like the committee that picked the 15 people to go to Kaunas?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, those were basically-- the committee was to regulate and do certain things to help with our private-- with the lives in the camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't have much to say in the factory, although they were managers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was a manager for a certain section.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the managers were consulted as to production schedules and all that.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
